title: Mahabharat - Star Plus -Hindi - 720P HD
description:
The story of the throne of Hastinapura, the kingdom ruled by the Kuru clan. The two collateral branches of the family that participate in the struggle of the throne of Hastinapura are the Kaurava and the Pandava.


season - 1 [720P HD]



1 Shantanu accepts Bhishma as son		  
2 Bhishma saves Vichitravirya		 
3 Bhishma defeats King Salva		  
4 Amba orders Bhishma to marry her		  
5 Two boys are born	
6 Bhishma has to make a choice	
7 Amba is reborn as Shikhandini
